dublin_core.dcvalue: The purpose of this conceptual paper is to introduce the concept of Mobile Social Networking Healthcare MSNet Health The paper defines MSNet Health and provides a working scenario of MSNet Health The paper suggests various potential domain area applications for MSNet Health such as diabetes antenatal education smoking cessation weight loss and arthritis Challenges and future research areas are also discussed
